      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the fortress metaphor, but i need to be more specific for the exam. can you explain the actual mechanics of how the bond works between the steel and the concrete? like, what's happening at the interface where the two materials meet to make sure they actually work together instead of just sliding past each other?",
